title: Ghatak / Lethal
subTitle: For his father's treatment, Kashi and his father move into a colony on the outskirts of Mumbai. But when Kashi sees a local gangster terrorise the colony, he decides to strike back.

title: Teri Kasam
subTitle: Dolly, a rich and spoilt woman, falls for Tony, a poor musician, and marries him. However, her arrogance begins to create problems in their marital life.

title: Pyar Ke Kabil
subTitle: Twin siblings are kept apart from each other after their parents separate. However, years later, the twins reunite and decide to switch roles in order to bring their parents back together.

title: Naya Kadam
subTitle: In a village ruled by Madhukar and Jaggu, who deprive the people of education so they can easily oppress them, Ramu manages to educate himself secretly with the help of a school teacher.

title: Majaal
subTitle: Vijay Kumar, an orphan, is brought up by an advocate. While he falls in love with his daughter and marries her, he struggles to cope with the humiliation he faces from her family.

title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Balidaan
subTitle: Police Inspector Vijay makes an enemy of bandit Ranga after he kills one of his men. After the vengeful Ranga wilfully abducts Vijay's wife and daughter, he must race against time to save his family.

title: Andhaa Kaanoon
subTitle: Two siblings, Vijay and Durga, vow to avenge the death of their parents. So, Durga becomes an inspector to punish the criminals, whereas Vijay breaks the law to achieve his goal.

title: Jungle
subTitle: Siddharth must swing into action when his girlfriend and her family are kidnapped and held for ransom by bandits. With danger lurking at every step, the family safari becomes a fight for survival.

title: Jungle
subTitle: Siddharth must swing into action when his girlfriend and her family are kidnapped and held for ransom by bandits. With danger lurking at every step, the family safari becomes a fight for survival.

title: Chingaari
subTitle: A novice postmaster in Rangpur unexpectedly becomes entangled in the complex lives of local sex workers, challenging his preconceptions.

title: Chingaari
subTitle: A novice postmaster in Rangpur unexpectedly becomes entangled in the complex lives of local sex workers, challenging his preconceptions.

title: Sikandar Sadak Ka
subTitle: When Sikander, a union worker, tries to stop his employer's misdeeds, the authorities jail him. After his release, Sikander is determined to seek revenge.

title: Mela
subTitle: Best mates Kishen and Shankar decide to help village belle Roopa avenge her family's death, but their friendship is tested in the process.

title: Hatya
subTitle: When Sagar finds a boy on the street, he brings him home and treats him well. But, he soon finds that the boy's mother has been killed and that he has become the prime suspect.

title: Kranti
subTitle: Sanga, a devout employee of Raja Laxman Singh, is falsely accused of killing him. He escapes prison and forms a group of revolutionaries with the sole aim of driving the British out of India.

title: Avtaar
subTitle: Avtaar leads a happy life with his wife, Radha, and his sons, Chander and Ramesh. However, consumed by their greed and ambitions, Avtaar's sons betray him but he soon reaches new heights of success.

title: Aakhri Ghulam
subTitle: Bheema and his family live under the tyranny of their master, Daulat Singh. But, when Bheema revolts, his love for his master's daughter is threatened.

title: Aakhri Ghulam
subTitle: Bheema and his family live under the tyranny of their master, Daulat Singh. But, when Bheema revolts, his love for his master's daughter is threatened.

title: Ranbanka
subTitle: Rahul, an ordinary engineer, comes to Mathura with his wife and son. However, when a gangster gets attracted to his wife and forces her to marry him, he tries to find a way to stop his advances.

title: Yes Boss
subTitle: Rahul's boss, Siddharth, is a womaniser who exploits Rahul into helping him win over Seema. However, Rahul ends up falling for Seema and is torn between his career aspirations and her.

title: Hatya: The Murder
subTitle: Ravi's father, Ratan, gets killed when he refuses to sell his land to Murugan, a wealthy businessman. Later, Ravi sets out to avenge the death of his father.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.

title: Khatron Ke Khiladi
subTitle: Balwant, a truck driver, is driven into the underworld as he wants to take revenge on the owners of the trucking company for the death of his brother.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.

title: Police Aur Mujrim
subTitle: After DSP Vishal arrests two thugs, their boss kidnaps the commissioner's daughter. But after Vishal rescues the girl and jails the thugs, they return to hurt Vishal and the commissioner's families.

title: Shiva Shakti
subTitle: Shiva forms a close friendship with Shakti when he comes to the city to earn money for his sister Kusum's wedding. However, he later vows to kill Shakti when Kusum becomes pregnant with his child.
